text: Chuvarez () is a rural locality (a village) in Cherkassky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 216 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 39 km from Ufa, 5 km from Cherkassy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Chuvarez
